Title: quicksearch: streamline single/multi pattern search plugin
Component: multisite
State: open
Date: 2014-07-03 14:44:05
Targetversion: future
Class: nastiness

The configurable quicksearch search filters use two different url generating concepts.
Single filters use predefined default templated - specified in sidebar.py.
Multi filters create the url out of functions or given url templates - specified in the filter defintion.

